text: Ra unako sathama aru du'i yuvakaharu pani jelama pravesa gare. Tiniharumadhye e'utale bhan'yo ki maile sapana dekheko chuh ki ma madirako nimti angura nicorirakheko chu. Arkole bhan'yoh ki maile pani sapana dekheko chu maile aphno ta'ukoma rotiharu bokeko chu ra panksiharule tyasabata kha'irakheka chan. Tasartha hamila'i yasako artha bhanidinus kinabhane hamile tapa'ila'i asala manisako rupama dekhirakheka chaum
